data.description: Brick home with metal roof on 12 acres offers a peaceful retreat with a variety of features. The property includes a well-equipped 30X40 shop building with electricity, water, a woodstove, as well as a toilet. Additionally, you'll find several outbuildings & carports making it ideal for gardening or small-scale farming. The property's history as a nursery/garden business is evident in the numerous fruit trees, including pear, apple, and blueberries. The house itself is made of brick and includes a storm cellar accessible from the garage, providing safety during inclement weather. This two-bedroom, two-bathroom home boasts walk-in closets, a spacious laundry room with built-ins, and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. The refrigerator and washer/dryer are included with the house. As well as a Home warranty provided by seller. Enjoy the sunroom, perfect for reading & relaxing or could possibly be a 3rd bedroom. While there is a well on the property, the home also has access to public water. This property offers a wonderful combination of comfortable living and ample outdoor space for gardening and relaxation.
